  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个简化版的Displayable Manager交互流程图。核心场景是：边缘节点收到事件后，先判断有没有可用的DisplayableManagers。如果没有就直接返回，有的话再区分是3D事件还是普通事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "DisplayableManagers",
        "Handle3DEvent",
        "FindCandidate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以起点是EdgeNode，然后第一个判断节点是检查DisplayableManagers是否为nullptr？如果是空，流程直接回到EdgeNode结束？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "if_start",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "DisplayableManagers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。如果不是空，再分支：如果是3D事件，走Handle3DEvent；其他情况走FindCandidate。Handle3DEvent处理完之后也要进入FindCandidate。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Handle3DEvent",
        "FindCandidate",
        "3D Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把初始分支和3D事件的处理路径画好了。FindCandidate这个节点我理解为\"寻找能处理事件的最近DM\"，然后需要再判断Closest是否为nullptr？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FindCandidate",
        "if_find",
        "Closest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。如果Closest是空，同样返回EdgeNode。否则进入UpdateFocus更新当前聚焦对象，然后再判断Focused是否为nullptr。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UpdateFocus",
        "if_focus",
        "Focused",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "UpdateFocus之后，如果Focused也是nullptr，流程结束；否则进入ProcessEvent处理交互，最后发送到MQTT Broker。这个Broker节点需要单独命名吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ProcessEvent",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，用IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker作为终点。另外注意ProcessEvent的节点名我想用ProcessInteraction，更贴合实际语义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ProcessEvent",
        "ProcessInteraction",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，所有判断节点用choice类型，ProcessEvent显示为ProcessInteraction。流程从EdgeNode出发，经过三次分支判断，最终要么提前返回，要么经ProcessInteraction到达MQTT Broker。请确认是否完整？",
      "elements_involved": [
